'''''Monru''''' was a group of at least four [[BFF-1 bulk freighter/Legends|BFF-1 bulk freighters]] that were delivering containers of supplies to the [[Imperial-class Star Destroyer/Legends|''Imperial''-class Star Destroyer]] ''[[Tormentor/Legends|Tormentor]]'' just as it came under [[Battle of Udnil II|attack]] near [[Udnil II]] by a [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] strike force consisting of [[T-65 X-wing starfighter/Legends|X-wings]] and [[BTL Y-wing starfighter/Legends|Y-wings]].

